It's okay if their's differeces in the 2 RPG's.)

Vulois

Vulois heard the explosions as the rubble of the mountain fell off 
from attack, and he laughed.

"Fools. We are too deep in the mountain. There attacks will not hurt 
us, they will only skim the mountain. It would take months to reach 
the tunnels. And if they try to come in and attack, they will get 
lost in the tunnels and wander the mountain forever. Come you three, 
we are almost at the main base."

Vulois kept walking.
